drm/amdgpu: Fix SDMA hang in prt mode v2

Fix SDMA hang in prt mode, clear XNACK_WATERMARK in reg SDMA0_UTCL1_WATERMK to avoid the issue

Affected ASICs: VEGA10 VEGA12 RV1 RV2

v2: add reg clear for SDMA1

